          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We at Paez care about becoming a more responsible brand. These past couple of years have been pivotal for us to start making much-deserved changes in our products that cause little less harm. We’re committed to being better every day and thus being transparent with every decision we make. <br/><br/>Each collection at Paez is proudly designed in Lisbon, Portugal. The production process begins in-house, with our design team carefully crafting each and every design to meet the highest standards of quality and innovation, bringing to life new and trendy shoes.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
