      "blocks": {
        "template--16679590920437__de1d68a7-5ece-4294-8555-c3b5c2a98d0a-167470665228bf0597-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We then produce our designs in Vietnam, with our partners who specialise in the sustainable development of footwear, mainly focusing on using responsible materials. They carefully select suppliers based on their certification in using recycled materials.<br/><br/>Since 2020, we’ve became 100% Vegan, meaning that we avoid animal ingredients in our textiles, shoes, and accessories. In 2021, we started incorporating high-quality textiles recycled by our suppliers certified by The Global Recycling Standard. </p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
