          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The GRS is an international standard that sets requirements for third-party certification of Recycled Content and a pedal from recycled pet bottle yarn. Like in 2023, every reference from our SS24 has recycled textiles incorporated in the shoe.<br/><br/>In 2023, we started a circularity program on our flagship stores. We invited our community to recycle their old Paez and give them a new life. This year, with our partner at Teco, we plan on developing an exclusive collection made from the rubber out of our in-sole.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        }
